---
name: Minimalist Mono
description: Style preset — Minimalist Mono
tags: [style, professional, aspect-auto]
---
Render as a stark, minimalist black-and-white diagram on a pure white background. Use only black lines, shapes, and text -- no color, no gradients, no fills. Lines should be clean and uniform weight. Use a simple, elegant sans-serif font. Maximize whitespace and let the structure breathe. The result should be austere and elegant -- like a diagram in an academic paper or a Dieter Rams design specification.
